  "text": "all of its factors in sequence: the index lists in each primitive operator must be coupled with the address lists in the given quantum register in order to calculate the qubits to be addressed, and the appropriate byte-code must be sent to the quantum device [CITATION_1] . This process may require ancilla qubits, which need to be spawned and reabsorbed transparently to the user. See appendix A.3 for more details on the steps taken when an operator is executed.",
